    <div class="card" id="main-card" style="display:none;">
        <h1>Hey <span id="display-name"></span> üíï</h1>
        <p>From my heart to your screen...<br>Will you be my Valentine? üåπ</p>
        <button id="yes" onclick="sayYes()">Yes üíñ</button>
        <button id="no" onmouseover="moveNo()">No üòÖ</button>
    </div>

    <div id="success-screen" style="display:none; z-index: 10;">
        <div class="card">
            <img src="us.jpg" id="photo" class="couple-photo" alt="Us">
            <h1>YAYYYY! üíñüéâ</h1>
            <p>You've made me the happiest person alive!</p>
            <button id="secret-btn" style="background:white; color:#ff4d6d;" onclick="showSecret()">Our Secret Note üíå</button>
            <p id="secret-text">
                "Every moment with you feels like a dream. You're the 'Iktara' to my soul. I love you, Jeniva! ‚ù§Ô∏è"
            </p>
        </div>
